name: Giving Tree
description: The Giving Tree is a fundraising and service club that focuses on raising money for a cause each quarter. We are bringing attention to smaller charities all throughout  Chicago. This will benefit the WY community by giving a chance to our students to be active members in their community.

announcements.title: Meetings
announcements.description: Club meetings take place once every other week on Tuesdays. in room 312.
